{"word":"χρηματιστής","slug":"χρηματιστής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χρηματιστής</b></el> <el>(χρημᾰτιστής, οῦ, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:χρηματίζω'><el>χρηματίζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a man in business, money-getter, trafficker</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>as <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a>, = <el>χρημᾰτιστικός</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}